市场平稳发展，为央行国债买卖操作提供适宜的市场环境。中国人民银行、财政部相关司局负责同志参加会议。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/70/v2-d5370cd7842e1e2def21f65c2cb4d7a8_1440w.avis?source=172ae18b&biz_tag=Post"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "87 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/791430888"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8It4isyda2ls8UEAMaCTExMTAzMjg3MyDH0Zi4BjAAOFBACXIJNzkxNDMwODg4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "10_1728616395.872749", "card_id": "Q_813571793", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 69}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "10 月 11 日三大股指集体低开，券商股集体走弱，熟悉的 A 股又回来了吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "滚动更新｜上证指数跌 0.43%，券商股集体走弱"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-0a8beb3d2f58b4ca6a43c5b33e73cb12_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "85 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/813571793"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8It4isyda2ls8UEAMaCTExMTA3MjQ2MCDSiqK4BjAAOFZACnIJODEzNTcxNzkzeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "11_1728616395.873126", "card_id": "Q_667726463", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 47}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "怎么看待国产车一定能追上甚至超越国际品牌的言论？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-11294f3d8eec8d0af72158f31f1e01ee_b.jpg"}, "metric